ontribution toward the development of the island's tourism. In order to cater for the multitude of travel and tourist requirements. By working today on the tourism and travel trends of tomorrow, anticipating and adapting to new customer trends, we are continually promoting major Mediterranean destinations such as Cyprus, Greece, Malta & Dubai. At the same time we play a role in preserving its unique culture and character, conscious always of the need to protect the environment. \n\nAeolos Cyprus Travel Ltd among other is the leading Inbound and Online operator in Cyprus with continual efforts to provide its clients with the most creative and innovative product ideas and services. Today, under the umbrella of Aeolos Cyprus Travel Ltd, there is a group of core activities, each one specializing in different areas of the business: 2Serve operates airport services, cargo handling and forwarding, Online B2C Travel portals such as Bookcyprus.com and Bookgreece.com focus on destination management (Hotel reservations, Transportation, Carhire, tour operator representation, organized excursions) and Belugga is active in Technology services such as Digital, Travel and Custom Services. \n\n**ONLINE TRAVEL SERVICES** Aeolos offers online travel services through www.bookcyprus.com, www.bookmalta.com and www.bookgreece.com combining our technological expertise with our many years of experience in tourism. \n\n**TECHNOLOGY SERVICES** Since 2011 part of Aeolos Group of Companies is also Belugga a digital agency based in Cyprus offering a great variety of services such us: Travel Booking System, Excursions Management System, Hotels online reservation, Web Development and Digital Services. \n\n**AIRPORT SERVICES** Another company created by Aeolos Group is 2-Serve which is a company offering a great variety of Airport services among them: PASSENGER SERVICES (Check-in and boarding control, Arrival and baggage services, Flight enquiries, Fully qualified staff) CARGO SERVICES (Cargo termi