"hash":"milzer_logowhite_138e17f5a0","ext":".png","mime":"image/png","size":1.87,"url":"/uploads/milzer_logowhite_138e17f5a0.png","previewUrl":null,"provider":"local","provider_metadata":null,"createdAt":"2024-10-31T16:37:16.175Z","updatedAt":"2024-10-31T16:37:16.175Z"}}},"country_flag":{"data":{"id":1,"attributes":{"countryIdentifier":"DE","countryName":"Germany","createdAt":"2023-06-16T09:57:14.007Z","updatedAt":"2023-06-16T09:57:58.577Z","publishedAt":"2023-06-16T09:57:58.571Z"}}},"cChainAddresses":[],"pChainAddresses":[]}},{"id":225,"attributes":{"contactEmail":"mbortolotto@mind3.ch","companyName":"MIND3","companyCountry":"Switzerland","companyWebsite":"https://www.mind3.ch/","contactFirstname":"Michele","contactLastname":"Bortolotto","contactPhone":null,"companyShortDescription":"MIND3, active since 2006, offers customized self-booking solutions to optimize tourism.\n","companyLongDescription":"Active since 2006, MIND3 specializes in the design and implementation of software projects. Our internal expertise encompasses technical design, software development, process analysis, and digital transformation. \n\nThis diverse skill set enables us to assemble the most suitable team based on the specific characteristics of each project we undertake. We are committed to providing our customers with specialized tools to support their operational processes. Our comprehensive approach to project management encompasses all phases, from requirement analysis to conception, design, and implementation of the final solution. \n\nWe utilize the Scrum methodology for project coordination and management, recognized as the most prevalent Agile method particularly suited for complex and innovative projects. This efficient integration of organizational capabilities, management skills, and cutting-edge technologies is the value we offer to businesses seeking to maximize results and optimize resource use, thereby enhancing their market competitiveness. \n\nOne of our key solutions is Travelplace, a reliable platform utilized by clients for over a decade. Travelplace emerged as an innovative solution, developed from extensive experience in integrating dynamic products for the travel sector. From the outset, the platform was designed as a booking engine capable of accessing a wide range of suppliers to offer tailored services, becoming an essential tool for clients in the Bed Bank segment. The first significant evolutionary step for Travelplace was a change in its underlying technology. This transition allowed the introduction of advanced features, including a Content Management System (CMS) that empowers clients to manage their web pages independently. Additionally, users can freely combine products into a personalized shopping cart, enabling the creation and purchase of dynamic packages. The platform has further evolved to allow the creation of preconfigured and closed packages, ready to be presented to end customers and easily bookable. This innovation was complemented by the ability to upload direct contracts with hotels, flights, tours, and other services, seamlessly integrating them with products from dynamic suppliers. In recent years, Travelplace has continued to enhance its management and automation features for the booking office, including managing quotation flows and optimizing operational efficiency. Communication tools have also been upgraded to better engage with clients, incorporating email and customizable prints, along with the ability to create fully customizable White Label solutions. Moreover, integration with various welfare management systems has further expanded the platform's capabilities, establishing it as a benchmark in the industry. \n\nThrough these advancements, MIND3 remains dedicated to driving innovation in the travel sector, providing customized self-booking solutions that optimize efficiency and enhance the overall customer experience.\n","isConsortiumMember":false,"createdAt":"2024-12-13T09:15:47.456Z","updatedAt