isshospitalitysolutions.ch","contactFirstname":"Andreas","contactLastname":"Klar","contactPhone":"+41766802505","companyShortDescription":"Swiss based advisory firm, specialised in hospitality projects and commercial performance.","companyLongDescription":"Founded in 2010, SHS Swiss Hospitality Solutions AG has established itself as the leading authority in Revenue Management and Online Distribution in the Swiss hospitality market. With a proven track record, SHS has successfully executed over 800 projects, serving a diverse clientele ranging from independent hotels to renowned hotel groups, including Dorint, Melia, Lindner, Meininger, and more. Our tailored solutions ensure measurable success across all scales of the hospitality sector. \n\nIn 2017, SHS expanded its impact by creating the:\n\n**SHS Academy**, a dedicated entity focused on training and professional development for industry leaders. Recognizing the need for innovation and collaboration, SHS launched \n\n**Swiss Distribution Day** in 2011, Switzerland’s first national industry event of its kind. Building on its success, the initiative evolved into the highly acclaimed \n\n**Swiss Innovation Day** in 2016, setting new standards for industry engagement. The SHS team also contributes to the academic landscape by serving as guest lecturers at prominent hotel schools and universities, shaping the next generation of hospitality professionals across Switzerland.\n","isConsortiumMember":false,"createdAt":"2025-04-03T14:51:26.286Z","updatedAt":"2025-04-04T11:20:53.046Z","publishedAt":"2025-04-04T11:20:53.038Z","logoBox":"noLogoBox","companyLinkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/shs-swiss-hospitality-solutions/","companyTwitter":null,"spotlightPartnerLink":null,"pChainAddress":null,"cChainAddress":null,"companyLogoColor":{"data":{"id":1135,"attributes":{"name":"SHS_MEHRZEILIG.png","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"width":184,"height":87,"formats":null,"hash":"SHS_MEHRZEILIG_7c88bb9d33","ext":".png","m